{"tid":1726264,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔會嚴重警告抱玩鬧心態的人   但係懇求您地","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T05:59:45.000Z","uid":195158,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b966095613c25b0488f21e2114a91d3d2023139c","tid":1726264,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"前事不提<br />\n因為大家都係手足<br />\n隔離個熱門post  如果語氣太剛強<br />\n睇得你唔舒服<br />\n請留低聽我兩句勸勉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動中，大家會Blackbloc蒙面<br />\n係對政權超級十分不信任同不滿嘅表現<br />\n面罩下，大家都保持七分理智，三分悲憤<br />\n而不是七分放縱，三分鬧玩心態<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一直所講核爆都唔割<br />\n就係完全信任手足 <br />\n行動嘅出發點係為運動好<br />\n想做就即管做<br />\nWhatever you do, we  trust</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n(信任得all or nothing，無乜柒高度信任架，正如你開始有半點懷疑另一半出軌，已經唔撚信囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBullshit完<br />\n聽多兩句<br />\n我地唔輸得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間、精神、金錢、健康、前途、甚至生命<br />\n無數手足已經付出過<br />\n<br />\n再講，人嘅最後一根稻草<br />\n信念同希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以失去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一旦失去<br />\n老一輩有能力就會諗移民外地<br />\n後生唔想走個批<br />\n就出現可預期嘅<span style=\"font-size: small;\">自殺潮、集體抑鬱</span><br />\n就算過返普通生活嘅，清算更加係接踵而來<br />\n<br />\n大家同輩，手足之情更甚<br />\n如果任何人曾經魯莽行事過<br />\n唔需要回望自責<br />\n但接下來就要步步為營，理性行事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"94f16159a07fd067daaf0b68d9601c019062dae7","tid":1726264,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"支持理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf615bd660f31d3dc64ce98e7ba209adf1f7632a","tid":1726264,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"支持理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d53d592183a12fe9aa932881b3feb003caa5509","tid":1726264,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b966095613c25b0488f2